        <para id="id1171785464529">Depending on your compiler/IDE, you should decide where to download and store source code files for processing. Prudence dictates that you create these folders as needed prior to downloading source code files. A suggested sub-folder for the <term>Bloodshed Dev-C++ 5 compiler/IDE</term> might be named:</para>
